msgid "<guilabel>Replay Gain Mode</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Replay Gain-modus</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:7738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to set the Replay Gain mode; <guilabel>Off</guilabel>, by "
"<guilabel>Track</guilabel>, or by <guilabel>Album</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Maakt het mogelijk de modus voor Replay Gain in te stellen; <guilabel>Uit</"
"guilabel>, per <guilabel>Track</guilabel> of per <guilabel>Album</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
